  <brief_title>A Study of Oral Sapacitabine and Oral Seliciclib in Patients With Advanced Solid Tumors</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I Study of Oral Sapacitabine and Oral Seliciclib in Patients With Advanced Solid Tumors</official_title>
